    "title": "Cómo identificar a un lector tóxico",
    "excerpt": "Dice que 'esto ya lo hizo Borges', menciona a Bolaño en cualquier conversación y desprecia los best sellers sin haberlos leído. ¿Te suena?",
    "content": "<div class=\"space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 italic\">Señales de alerta para detectar a tiempo a ese lector que arruina clubes de lectura, sobremesas y grupos de WhatsApp.</p><div class=\"grid gap-4\"><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-orange-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm\">1</span><p class=\"text-gray-700\">Dice <span class=\"font-bold text-red-600\">\"esto ya lo hizo Borges\"</span>.</p></div><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-50 to-amber-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-orange-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm\">2</span><p class=\"text-gray-700\">Menciona a <span class=\"font-bold text-orange-600\">Bolaño en cualquier conversación</span>.</p></div><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 to-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm\">3</span><p class=\"text-gray-700\"><span class=\"font-bold text-amber-600\">Corrige citas ajenas</span>.</p></div><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-lime-50 to-green-50 border-l-4 border-lime-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-lime-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm\">4</span><p class=\"text-gray-700\">Desprecia los <span class=\"font-bold text-lime-600\">best sellers sin haberlos leído</span>.</p></div><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-50 to-cyan-50 border-l-4 border-teal-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm\">5</span><p class=\"text-gray-700\">Usa palabras como <span class=\"font-bold text-teal-600\">\"inane\" o \"epifanía\"</span> solo para oírse culto.</p></div><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-50 to-blue-50 border-l-4 border-cyan-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-cyan-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm\">6</span><p class=\"text-gray-700\">Mide su valor por el <span class=\"font-bold text-cyan-600\">grosor de los libros</span> que lee.</p></div><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm\">7</span><p class=\"text-gray-700\">Dice que <span class=\"font-bold text-blue-600\">odia TikTok</span>, pero le dedica hilos enteros a explicar por qué.</p></div><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-50 to-violet-50 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm\">8</span><p class=\"text-gray-700\">Se ofende si confundes un <span class=\"font-bold text-indigo-600\">autor menor con un autor muerto</span>.</p></div><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-50 to-purple-50 border-l-4 border-violet-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-violet-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm\">9</span><p class=\"text-gray-700\">Afirma que <span class=\"font-bold text-violet-600\">ya no se escribe como antes</span>.</p></div><div class=\"group flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-pink-50 border-l-4 border-purple-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-purple-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm\">10</span><p class=\"text-gray-700\">Cree que <span class=\"font-bold text-purple-600\">leer lo hace mejor persona</span>.</p></div></div></div>",
